title: Dreambaby Chelsea Auto-Close Security Baby Safety Gate (38-46 Inch)
features: QUICK AND EASY OPERATION - With the Chelsea pressure-mounted gate, installation is a breeze and using it is even easier. The gate allows for one-handed operation and the double action locking feature helps keep even the most curious toddlers at bay.

SMART STAY-OPEN, AUTO-CLOSE - Doing laundry, entertaining guests or carrying in the groceries? With the convenience of the Smart Stay-Open feature, the Chelsea gate can be made to stay open to allow for seamless movement throughout the home. For all other times, it has a handy Auto-Close feature, ensuring that the gate reliably closes every time.

EZY-CHECK INDICATOR- For added security, the EZY-Check indicator will help you identify if your gate is securely closed with just a quick glance. **Tip: The EZY-Check indicator is also great for helping to make sure that your gate is properly installed.
